metadata.name: Walrus #1
metadata.description: From Tuskgard to the Metaverse... The Acid Walrus is a collection of 10.000 randomly generated and unique NFTs in the Ethereum Blockchain. Each Walrus allows its owner to be part of the active holders and enjoy different perks like Premium Member benefits, Airdrops, Giveaways and other upcoming features we would like to explore. Visit www.TheAcidWalrus.com for more.
